# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:12
translate portuguese izzy13_8ca62be9:

    # gl "Hey Twig! Guess what? I got the job!"
    gl "Ei, Twig! Adivinha só? Consegui o emprego!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:13
translate portuguese izzy13_68c72b69:

    # pc "Hey, congratulations!"
    pc "Ei, parabéns!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:14
translate portuguese izzy13_5a2b96eb:

    # pc "I guess that means you'll be leaving soon, Mari?"
    pc "Acho que isso significa que vais partir em breve, Mari?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:15
translate portuguese izzy13_d83a5365:

    # fr "Yeah, I'm going to train her for a little while, then I'm done."
    fr "Sim, vou treiná-la por um tempo, depois estou livre."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:16
translate portuguese izzy13_1591b993:

    # fr "It's a little sad, but I'm glad that Jackson has a good person to take my position."
    fr "É um pouco triste, mas fico contente por o Jackson ter uma boa pessoa para ocupar o meu lugar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:17
translate portuguese izzy13_93f32351:

    # gl "Thanks, girl. I appreciate that."
    gl "Obrigada, miúda. Agradeço isso."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:18
translate portuguese izzy13_0ce62e11:

    # gl "Well, let's get your order in."
    gl "Bem, vamos fazer o teu pedido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:21
translate portuguese izzy13_5e8dd55b:

    # "Izzy leads me back to my booth, with Mari trailing along behind her, supervising."
    "A Izzy leva-me de volta à minha mesa, com a Mari a seguir atrás dela, a supervisionar."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:22
translate portuguese izzy13_44f9ac2a:

    # gl "So what are you having today?"
    gl "Então, o que vais comer hoje?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:23
translate portuguese izzy13_6c37c9c9:

    # pc "Cheeseburger with everything, fries, and a coke."
    pc "Cheeseburger com tudo, batatas fritas e uma Coca-Cola."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:24
translate portuguese izzy13_61e49ea3:

    # gl "Simple. I like it. Give me a few minutes."
    gl "Simples. Gosto disso. Dá-me uns minutos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:27
translate portuguese izzy13_12885faf:

    # "Izzy rushes off to the back to put my order in."
    "A Izzy corre para as traseiras para registar o meu pedido."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:28
translate portuguese izzy13_c78badbd:

    # pc "So how are things going? How is she doing?"
    pc "Então, como estão as coisas? Como é que ela se está a sair?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:29
translate portuguese izzy13_85b43910:

    # fr "She's doing great so far. Jackson likes her a lot."
    fr "Está a sair-se muito bem até agora. O Jackson gosta muito dela."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:30
translate portuguese izzy13_278c283a:

    # fr "She's pretty sassy. Jackson loves that."
    fr "Ela é bastante atrevida. O Jackson adora isso."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:31
translate portuguese izzy13_c478ef3e:

    # pc "Good. I'm really happy it's working out."
    pc "Ótimo. Estou muito feliz por estar a correr bem."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:32
translate portuguese izzy13_ecc2451e:

    # fr "Me too!"
    fr "Eu também!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:33
translate portuguese izzy13_a3a72879:

    # fr "Well, I better get back to helping her. I'll talk to you later, [pcname]."
    fr "Bem, é melhor voltar a ajudá-la. Falo contigo mais tarde, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:34
translate portuguese izzy13_53fa2ef6:

    # pc "Okay, see ya."
    pc "Ok, até logo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:37
translate portuguese izzy13_69b02f38:

    # "Mari leaves and I play on my phone for a few minutes until Izzy returns with my food."
    "A Mari sai e eu fico a brincar com o telemóvel por alguns minutos até a Izzy voltar com a minha comida."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:40
translate portuguese izzy13_3cd8bfcc:

    # gl "Got your burger ready, Twig. Enjoy."
    gl "O teu hambúrguer está pronto, Twig. Aproveita."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:41
translate portuguese izzy13_97e892af:

    # pc "Thanks! I'm sure I will."
    pc "Obrigado! Tenho a certeza que vou."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:42
translate portuguese izzy13_8dc0436a:

    # gl "So you and Mari have a thing going on?"
    gl "Então, tu e a Mari estão a namorar?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:43
translate portuguese izzy13_999c143d:

    # pc "Yeah, we've been dating some."
    pc "Sim, temos saído um pouco."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:44
translate portuguese izzy13_f21ed68a:

    # gl "Man, she's so hot."
    gl "Caramba, ela é tão gira."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:45
translate portuguese izzy13_a996b478:

    # gl "We should all three get together sometime, you know?"
    gl "Devíamos os três sair juntos um dia destes, sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:46
translate portuguese izzy13_f945ea47:

    # pc "Yeah maybe. We'll see."
    pc "Sim, talvez. Veremos."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:47
translate portuguese izzy13_0827ec33:

    # gl "Anyway, let me know if you need anything. I gotta go take care of those assholes over there."
    gl "De qualquer forma, avisa-me se precisares de alguma coisa. Tenho de ir tratar daqueles idiotas ali."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:48
translate portuguese izzy13_49912e7a:

    # pc "Alright, I will."
    pc "Está bem, avisarei."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:51
translate portuguese izzy13_410fc4ec:

    # "Izzy goes to help other customers and I eat my meal."
    "O Izzy vai ajudar outros clientes e eu como a minha refeição."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:54
translate portuguese izzy13_1afb6a34:

    # "Then a few minutes later, Izzy and Mari return."
    "Alguns minutos depois, o Izzy e a Mari regressam."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:55
translate portuguese izzy13_b99c5a01:

    # gl "Did you like your burger?"
    gl "Gostaste do teu hambúrguer?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:56
translate portuguese izzy13_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:57
translate portuguese izzy13_d2f1177a:

    # gl "I know, right? They're so fucking good."
    gl "Eu sei, não é? São tão bons."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:58
translate portuguese izzy13_4a0f9f0f:

    # gl "I'm going to end up eating so many, working here. My ass is gonna get {i}fat{/i}!"
    gl "Vou acabar por comer tantos, a trabalhar aqui. O meu rabo vai ficar {i}gordo{/i}!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:59
translate portuguese izzy13_bad98252:

    # gl "How do you stay so fit, Mari?"
    gl "Como é que te manténs tão em forma, Mari?"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:60
translate portuguese izzy13_2202a21b:

    # fr "Benefits of being vegetarian."
    fr "São as vantagens de ser vegetariana."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:61
translate portuguese izzy13_03e1f782:

    # gl "Well I sure as hell ain't doing that!"
    gl "Bem, eu com certeza que não vou fazer isso!"

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:62
translate portuguese izzy13_481c466b:

    # gl "Anyways, have a good day, Twig. I'll see you later."
    gl "De qualquer forma, tem um bom dia, Twig. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:63
translate portuguese izzy13_1af352a6:

    # fr "Yeah, bye [pcname]. Thanks for coming in."
    fr "Sim, adeus [pcname]. Obrigado por teres vindo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:66
translate portuguese izzy13_afdbb1fc:

    # "They start to walk away, and Izzy looks back at me."
    "Eles começam a afastar-se e a Izzy olha para trás, para mim."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:67
translate portuguese izzy13_65d07413:

    # gl "You better give me a good tip. I was downright fucking pleasant."
    gl "É melhor dares-me uma boa gorjeta. Fui absolutamente simpática."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:68
translate portuguese izzy13_8a5abc7f:

    # pc "I'll give you more than the tip."
    pc "Vou dar-te mais do que a gorjeta."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:69
translate portuguese izzy13_8f001d5e:

    # gl "Don't tease me, Twig. I have to work 'til closing today."
    gl "Não me provoquem, Twig. Hoje tenho de trabalhar até ao fecho."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:70
translate portuguese izzy13_864b9473:

    # pc "Have fun."
    pc "Diverte-te."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:71
translate portuguese izzy13_4772f020:

    # gl "Yeah, yeah. See ya."
    gl "Sim, sim. Até logo."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:74
translate portuguese izzy13_2cf41d4f:

    # "With a smile, I leave a generous tip on the table and leave."
    "Com um sorriso, deixo uma gorjeta generosa na mesa e saio."

# game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:75
translate portuguese izzy13_b9414cfd:

    # "It's good to see Izzy doing well. I hope the job works out for her."
    "É bom ver a Izzy a dar-se bem. Espero que o emprego corra bem para ela."

translate portuguese strings:

    # game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:1
    old "You'll need to progress far enough with Izzy that she is looking for a job. You will also have to progress far enough with Mari that she tells you she is leaving Jackson Burger."
    new "Terás de avançar o suficiente com a Izzy para que ela esteja à procura de emprego. Também terás de avançar o suficiente com a Mari para que ela te diga que vai deixar o Jackson Burger."

    # game/Scenes/Izzy/izzy13.rpy:2
    old "Have conversations with Izzy asking what kind of job she is looking for, then have the conversation to suggest Jackson Burger. Then this scene will happen when you next go to Jackson Burger."
    new "Conversa com a Izzy perguntando que tipo de emprego ela procura e, depois, sugere-lhe o Jackson Burger. Então, esta cena acontecerá na próxima vez que fores ao Jackson Burger."

